<p style="margin: 0 0 0 0">
	<h4>If you were arrested in a different county in IL:</h4>
	search for your zip code <a href="http://www.illinoislegalaid.org/index.cfm?fuseaction=home.dsp_content&contentID=7064#a=legalhelp">here</a> and contact the appropriate legal aid organization

</p>
</div>
